去到醫院先知骨裂<br />\n打左幾個月石膏同做物理治療<br />\n都係痛撚到仆街"},{"pid":"fccc99ed53aa9bc000d0b6db49f876613a1640a4","tid":557633,"uid":78901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱小學開學前一日下巴插到木床角落 縫左幾針 果時唔知有冇落麻醉藥 完全依家都仲記得果種痛 所以依家點都唔會比人掂下巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人哋問你條疤點嚟你可以講同人隻抽俾入升龍拳爆下巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd9af407d4849633b202c8ece5841a2c28b5318","tid":557633,"uid":78901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鉛芯插入手指甲，去醫院麻醉針直接拮入手指再撬開指甲拎翻出嚟</blockquote><br />\n滿清十大酷刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0340e840b846cdd591c8e1a6f6387e16ac9c4ce8","tid":557633,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"切J"},{"pid":"2bd11951fd054ce196f4a2c0255c76ee8bd14529","tid":557633,"uid":86988,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"打自由搏擊俾人低炒粒蛋，當場痛到縮埋一舊，眼水鼻水口水冷汗一次過出曬，好大力呼吸，feel到就暈<br />\n好彩冇爆丸，不過要拐下拐下咁翻屋企"},{"pid":"6994b25693294431b7c79c4b726b0bb45ff80d02","tid":557633,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"生蛇<br />\n屌你老味成個星期冇覺好訓<br />\n啪完止痛藥 訓到咁上下藥力一過就會痛醒<br />\n個陣仲要係格拉底個個位最痛 個種神經痛一世仔唔會忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a677b871a576a52c9c14393c7fde7312daeba18","tid":557633,"uid":53254,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"第一次俾男友，開頭好緊張，係咁縮<br />\n佢一野咀埋黎，同一隊入黎<br />\n<br />\n俾d外來野入侵既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但屌屌下又幾爽"},{"pid":"c2acc19269a6de2f10f81458a60eb1c6c4230ba1","tid":557633,"uid":